From stefan prague Stefan Fielding Isaacs Subject Racelist WHO WHAT WHERE Greetings fellow motorcycle roadracing enthusiasts BACKGROUND The racing listserver contains discussions devoted to racing and racing related This is a pretty broad interest Individuals have a variety of backgrounds motojournalism roadracing from the perspective of pit crew and racers engineering motosports The size of the list grows We are currently at a little over one hundred and eighty five members with contributors from New Zealand Australia Germany France England Canada Finland Switzerland and the United The list was formed October in response to a perceived need to both provide technical discussion of riding at the edge of performance roadracing and to improve on the very low signal to noise ratio found in Anyone is free to Discussion is necessarily limited by the rules of the list to issues related to racing motorcycles and is to be flame free HOW TO GET THE DAILY DISTRIBUTION You are welcome to To subscribe send your request to race request Traffic currently runs between five and twenty five messages per day depending on the topic NB Please do not send your subscription request to the list After you have contacted the list administrator you will receive an RSVP Please respond to this request in a timely manner so that you can be added to the The request is generated in order to insure that there is a valid mail pathway to your Upon receipt of your RSVP you will be added to either the daily or digest distribution as per your initial request HOW TO GET THE DIGEST DISTRIBUTION It is possible to receive the list in 'digest'ed form a single email message The RoadRacing Digest is mailed out whenever it contains enough interesting Given the frequency of postings this appears to be about every other Should you wish to receive the list via digest once every or so please send a subscription request to digest request HOW TO POST TO THE LIST This is an open To post an article to the list send to race Depending on how mail is set up at your site you may or may not see the mail that you have If you want to see it though this isn't necessarily a guarantee that it went out you can include a metoo line in your file on UNIX based mail systems BOUNCES Because I haven't had the time or the inclination to replace the list distribution mechanism we still have a problem with bounces returning to the poster of a Occasionally sites or users go off line either leaving their place of employment prematurely or hardware problems and you will receive bounces from the race Check the headers carefully and if you find that the bounce originated at Sun from whence I administer this list contact me through my administration hat race request If not ignore the OTHER LISTS Two strokes Harleys or uunet watmath thinkage harley request European bikes in body of message write subscribe euro moto thanks be seeing you Rich race list administrator rich Stefan Fielding Isaacs office fax dba Art Science Books By Design voice pager AMA CCS currently providing consulting writing services to Gain Technology Verity